hopobject.body: A company car natmedsol.com The governor also objected to a decision by the White House Office of Management and Budget to apply federal sequestration measures to the RESTORE Act trust fund. That could delay the use of some of the fine money for several years. Jindal also said duplication of scientific studies and permit applications and approvals “are not what the public had in mind when they stepped out in strong support of the RESTORE Act, and it does not correspond to the urgency we have on the Gulf Coast.”
